cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SE, cs.DS 

This paper is likely to belong to the category of Computer Security (cs.CR) as it deals with the detection of unknown malware. It may also belong to the categories of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Machine Learning (cs.LG) as the authors have used classification methods to detect malware. Additionally, it may belong to the category of Software Engineering (cs.SE) as the authors have partitioned the dataset to select features. Finally, it may also belong to the category of Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS) as the authors have used a partitioning approach to improve the accuracy of malware detection.
